{
  "id": "6569ceffe298570023b7542f",
  "title": "「寒い」と「さみしい」の関係",
  "created": 1701433088,
  "updated": 1701484541,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6569ceffe298570023b7542f",
      "text": "「寒い」と「さみしい」の関係",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701433088
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ceffaff09e0000e2c1e5",
      "text": "from [2023/12/01]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701433088
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ceffaff09e0000e2c1e6",
      "text": "「寒い」と「さみしい」の関係",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701484346
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ceffaff09e0000e2c1e7",
      "text": " [「寒い」と「さみしい」の関係]が気になって調べた[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701433088
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ceffaff09e0000e2c1e8",
      "text": "  [錆]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701433088
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ceffaff09e0000e2c1e9",
      "text": "  [わび]、[さび]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701433088
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ceffaff09e0000e2c1ea",
      "text": "  [すさぶ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701433088
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ceffaff09e0000e2c1eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701433088
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ceffaff09e0000e2c1ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433088,
      "updated": 1701433088
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b001",
      "text": "from [2023/12/01]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b002",
      "text": "「寒い」と「さみしい」の関係",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569d577aff09e00009afec1",
      "text": "　[さぶ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701434744,
      "updated": 1701434747
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b003",
      "text": "\thttps://ja.wiktionary.org/wiki/さぶ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b004",
      "text": " \t古典日本語",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b005",
      "text": " \t\t動詞:さぶ【寂ぶ、荒ぶ】",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b006",
      "text": "    寂しく思う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569e6705e90c00000622d2c",
      "text": "    　[うらさぶる心さまねし久方の天のしぐれのながらふ見れば][cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1701439087,
      "updated": 1701439099
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b007",
      "text": "    古くなる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b008",
      "text": "    色褪せる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b009",
      "text": " \t\t動詞:さぶ【錆ぶ】",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b00a",
      "text": " \t  錆が生じる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b00b",
      "text": " \t https://ja.wiktionary.org/wiki/さぶし",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b00c",
      "text": " \t \t（上代）寂しい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b00d",
      "text": " \tこの時期の温度が低いことによる「寒い」に相当する言葉は？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b00e",
      "text": " 　「寒し」とは言っている[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b00f",
      "text": " \t 古代日本語（上代）における温度が低い「寒い」の例（[日国]）[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b010",
      "text": " \t >(1)温度がいちじるしく低く感じられるさま。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b011",
      "text": " \t 略",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b012",
      "text": " \t　>(ロ)気温が不快なほどに低いさま。また、そのように感じるさま。寒気を感じるさま。《季・冬》",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b013",
      "text": "   > ＊日本書紀〔７２０〕天智称制一二月（北野本訓）「高麗国は寒（サムイ）こと極（きはま）て倶（え）凍（こほれ）り」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b014",
      "text": "    「寒」の訓",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b015",
      "text": "    　古辞書の方は後ほど[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b016",
      "text": "    　https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/2605220/1/1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b017",
      "text": "   >＊万葉集〔８Ｃ後〕一七・三九四五「秋の夜は暁（あかとき）左牟之（サムシ）白たへの妹が衣手着むよしもがも〈大伴池主〉",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569d595aff09e00009afec2",
      "text": "  どっちも「さむい」「さむし」と「む」を使ってて、「さぶ」ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701434774,
      "updated": 1701434811
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b018",
      "text": "\t\t　「寒い」と「さみしい」が同じ語源という説はなんか怪しいなあという気持ち[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701434813
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b019",
      "text": "\t　\t　+1[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701484434
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b01a",
      "text": "　\t\t　[国立国語研究所の広報室の見解だと、「現代の言語の科学としての日本語学にとって、語源論は、その中心的な研究対象や範疇に入らない」]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b01b",
      "text": "　\t[さぶし]　の語釈[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701434833
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b01c",
      "text": "　\t　>本来あるべき状態になく、また、本来備わっているはずのものが欠けていて、気持が満たされない。さびしい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b01d",
      "text": "   > ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b01e",
      "text": "   > ＊[続日本紀]‐宝亀二年〔７７１〕二月二二日・[宣命]「歳時積り往くまにまに、佐夫之岐（サブシキ）事のみし、彌（いよよ）益（まさ）るべきかも」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b01f",
      "text": "   > ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b020",
      "text": "   > ＊万葉集〔８Ｃ後〕四・四八六「山の端（は）にあぢ群（むら）騒き行くなれどわれは左夫思（サブシ）ゑ君にしあらねば〈斉明天皇〉」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b021",
      "text": "   > ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b022",
      "text": "   > ＊万葉集〔８Ｃ後〕五・八七八「言ひつつも後こそ知らめとのしくも佐夫志計（サブシケ）めやも君坐（いま）さずして〈山上憶良〉」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b023",
      "text": "  [マ音・バ音の音変化]が関わっていそう[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701433114
    },
    {
      "id": "6569cf19aff09e0000d6b024",
      "text": "\t\t\tなるほど、確かに活用形にも差がある[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701433114,
      "updated": 1701484219
    },
    {
      "id": "656a96b8aff09e0000e2c21a",
      "text": "\t\t\t>近世に全国のあちこちで「む」から「ぶ」への音韻変化が生じたようだ。そして[言海]に「さぶい」は無く...",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1701484219,
      "updated": 1701484466
    },
    {
      "id": "656a97a0aff09e0000e2c21d",
      "text": "\t\t\t寒いの意味の「さぶい」は近世に生じた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701484451,
      "updated": 1701484486
    },
    {
      "id": "6569d5e9aff09e00009afec3",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/cdc52ee61a7be63dfcf7f1736a813ef5]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701434857,
      "updated": 1701435435
    },
    {
      "id": "6569d82baff09e0000e2c1ed",
      "text": "\t700~800年ごろには既に分かれていて、混ざってない感じ[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701435435,
      "updated": 1701435486
    },
    {
      "id": "656a969faff09e0000e2c219",
      "text": "\t\t「さぶし」が「さびし」「さみしい」と変化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701484193,
      "updated": 1701484496
    },
    {
      "id": "656a97cfaff09e0000e2c21f",
      "text": "\t\t「さむし」が近世に「さぶし」と変化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701484497,
      "updated": 1701484530
    },
    {
      "id": "656a97cdaff09e0000e2c21e",
      "text": "\t\tその後で「この二つは似てる！」となった感",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701484496,
      "updated": 1701484541
    },
    {
      "id": "656a9722aff09e0000e2c21b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701484325,
      "updated": 1701484359
    },
    {
      "id": "6569d973aff09e0000e2c1f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701435764,
      "updated": 1701440105
    },
    {
      "id": "6569d848aff09e0000e2c1ee",
      "text": "[https://youtu.be/nUAMUPqqHWk]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701435464,
      "updated": 1701435759
    },
    {
      "id": "6569d96eaff09e0000e2c1f0",
      "text": "　入力欄はEnterキーで出してます",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701435759,
      "updated": 1701440019
    },
    {
      "id": "6569ea13aff09e0000eefa09",
      "text": "　拡大縮小はMacのタッチパッドで二本指ジェスチャー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701440019,
      "updated": 1701440042
    },
